chore: do not gate umbrella coverage on this plugin

Use test_coverage: [summary: [threshold: 0]] so the umbrella mix test --cover
step reports this plugin coverage in the summary without failing the build.
The summary threshold value is the actual gate in Elixir; 90 would hard-fail
below 90% (this plugin is independently published and tested).

